---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us — ToolHub" description="Learn about ToolHub, our philosophy, privacy-first commitment, and why we offer free online calculators and browser utilities.">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-heading font-extrabold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl mb-6">About ToolHub</h1>
    
    <p class="lead text-lg text-muted">
      ToolHub is a collection of free, simple, and high-performance browser-based calculators and utility tools designed to make everyday computations fast and stress-free.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
      Our mission is to democratize basic calculations. Whether you are estimating your monthly loan EMI, evaluating your body mass index (BMI), calculating your college GPA, or converting units of measurement, ToolHub provides accurate, instant answers with zero friction.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Privacy Commitment</h2>
    <p>
      We believe that your personal data belongs to you. Unlike other utility platforms, **ToolHub runs 100% of its calculations client-side in your web browser**. 
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>No values you enter are ever uploaded to a database or sent to a remote server.</li>
      <li>Your calculations are private, secure, and cannot be intercepted or tracked.</li>
      <li>The site works seamlessly offline once loaded, ensuring reliability.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Open & Free</h2>
    <p>
      All tools on ToolHub are entirely free to use. There are no premium gates, no mandatory subscriptions, and no registration flows. We finance our server and hosting costs through unobtrusive advertisements that comply with the highest user experience standards.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      Have feedback, a bug report, or a suggestion for a new calculator? Please visit our <a href="/contact/" class="text-primary hover:underline">Contact Page</a> to get in touch with our development team.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
